 properties of the\nlatter have been transmitted by the genetic code while the universe element\nabundance curve changed as the galaxies aged.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 May 2016 09:42:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-30"}
